<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Family Heritage Platform – API</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: #0f172a;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .card {
            background: #1e293b;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 3rem;
            max-width: 640px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #f1f5f9;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #14532d;
            color: #86efac;
            border: 1px solid #16a34a;
            border-radius: 99px;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        .links {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .link-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background: #0f172a;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
            text-align: left;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .link-row:hover {
            border-color: #6366f1;
            background: #1e1b4b;
        }

        .link-icon {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .link-text strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #f1f5f9;
        }

        .link-text span {
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .link-arrow {
            margin-left: auto;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .endpoint-list {
            background: #0f172a;
            border: 1px solid #1e293b;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .endpoint-list h3 {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .endpoint {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.3rem 0;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b;
        }

        .endpoint:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

        .method {
            font-size: 0.68rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            min-width: 44px;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        }

        .get  { background: #1d4ed8; color: #bfdbfe; }
        .post { background: #15803d; color: #bbf7d0; }
        .patch { background: #b45309; color: #fde68a; }
        .delete { background: #be123c; color: #fecdd3; }

        .path { color: #94a3b8; font-family: monospace; }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #334155;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="logo">🌳</div>
        <h1>Family Heritage Platform</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">A private, multi-branch family history API for building<br>and preserving your family's genealogy across generations.</p>

        <div class="badge">● API SERVER RUNNING</div>

        <div class="links">
            <a href="/api/docs.html" class="link-row">
                <span class="link-icon">📖</span>
                <span class="link-text">
                    <strong>Interactive API Docs</strong>
                    <span>Swagger UI – browse, test and explore all endpoints</span>
                </span>
                <span class="link-arrow">→</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/api/docs.jsonld" class="link-row">
                <span class="link-icon">🔗</span>
                <span class="link-text">
                    <strong>OpenAPI Specification</strong>
                    <span>Machine-readable API schema (JSON-LD)</span>
                </span>
                <span class="link-arrow">→</span>
            </a>
            <a href="http://localhost:8080" target="_blank" class="link-row">
                <span class="link-icon">🗄️</span>
                <span class="link-text">
                    <strong>phpMyAdmin</strong>
                    <span>Browse and manage the MySQL database</span>
                </span>
                <span class="link-arrow">↗</span>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="endpoint-list">
            <h3>Available Endpoints</h3>
            <div class="endpoint">
                <span class="method post">POST</span>
                <span class="path">/api/auth/login</span>
            </div>
            <div class="endpoint">
                <span class="method post">POST</span>
                <span class="path">/api/auth/refresh</span>
            </div>
            <div class="endpoint">
                <span class="method get">GET</span>
                <span class="path">/api/persons</span>
            </div>
            <div class="endpoint">
                <span class="method post">POST</span>
                <span class="path">/api/persons</span>
            </div>
            <div class="endpoint">
                <span class="method get">GET</span>
                <span class="path">/api/persons/{id}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="endpoint">
                <span class="method patch">PATCH</span>
                <span class="path">/api/persons/{id}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="endpoint">
                <span class="method delete">DELETE</span>
                <span class="path">/api/persons/{id}</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            Symfony 7 · API Platform 4 · PHP 8.3 · MySQL 8 · JWT Auth
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

